        "html": "=<h2>Hello {{ $node[\"Webhook - Application Submitted\"].json.body.candidateName }},</h2>\n\n<p>Thank you for your interest in RecruForce2 and for applying for the <strong>{{ $node[\"Webhook - Application Submitted\"].json.body.jobTitle }}</strong> position.</p>\n\n<p>After reviewing your profile, we regret to inform you that we will not be moving forward with your application at this time as your current skills do not fully align with our specific requirements for this role.</p>\n\n<p>However, we will keep your profile in our database for future opportunities that may better match your background. We wish you the very best of luck with your professional search.</p>\n\n<br>\n<p>Best regards,<br>\n<strong>The RecruForce2 Recruitment Team</strong></p>",
